{"tid":57032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣麗芸引述父親：國家要發展，就靠今天執政黨","createTime":"2016-12-27T16:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T17:31:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c61db26f6e084cc594498056e6065602c84ff0a2","tid":57032,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161227/s00001/1482812725156SL4_BC3838022058D074D3E47FB438D21A06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161227%2Fs00001%2F1482812725156SL4_BC3838022058D074D3E47FB438D21A06.jpg&h=b777a183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港人身分認同問題一直引起關注。民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸今朝就喺facebook分享今年2月內地音樂節目《音樂大師課》有少年唱出《我的中國心》一段，感慨話「每次聽到這歌曲，我會流淚&hellip;&hellip;」佢仲分享自己嘅「中國心」係如何煉成添。<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸話，1983年第一次到內地，眼看當時落後嘅內地，心裏湧溢住講唔出嘅酸痛，又慶幸自己生於香港，所以就問父親蔣震「我們能為國家做什麼？」<br />\n<br />\n佢引述父親話，「國家要發展，就靠今天的執政黨，如果執政黨倒下，社會就亂，老百姓生活會更苦；作為香港人，為了國家發展，為了同胞有更好的民生就必須積極貢獻&hellip;&hellip;我們沒有選擇&hellip;&hellip;因為祖先早已把我們的一切烙&hellip;&hellip;下&hellip;&hellip;中&hellip;&hellip;國&hellip;&hellip;印&hellip;&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸父親蔣震係著名工業家，創辦咗震雄集團，2005年獲頒大紫荊勳章。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161227/s00001/1482810494711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161227%2Fs00001%2F1482810494711&d=1AXYoDBdgTSqOkzXM491u3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9ea02345\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161227%2Fs00001%2F1482810494711&h=3d855050\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161227/s00001/1482810494711</a>"},{"pid":"6749770727797c71a36fd381c53c3b113e62ad5b","tid":57032,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:56:28.000Z","msg":"國民黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831b